      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIGHTY SCAR (1) comes off a handy 28.75 placing at this track over 510m. Expected to push the clock again here. FANTASTIC ZOHAN (7) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split, grabbed late but holding on to a placing when a 1.5 lengths second (26.04) over 460m at Warragul. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Must be included in calculations. FOLLOW THE SUN (2) had been super consistent recording three placings in a row before he was rewarded with a win last time, scoring at this track over 435m (24.78). Deserves serious consideration again. EAGLE BREAD (5) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when second (26.16) in a Grade 5 over 460m at Warragul.",
